	(131,1,'2016-12-05 14:54:53','2016-12-05 14:54:53','Cetis specialises in technology innovation and interoperability standards in learning, education and training. We are active in the development and implementation of open standards and represent our clients in national, European and global standards bodies and industry consortia. We have been instrumental in developing and promoting the adoption of technology and standards for course advertising, open education resources, assessment, and student data management, in order to open new markets and create opportunities for innovation. We adopt and promote open approaches and believe data, standards and technology should be openly available.We work with our partners to develop policy and strategy, providing impartial and independent advice on technology and standards.','Cetis LLP','','inherit','closed','closed','','89-revision-v1','','','2016-12-05 14:54:53','2016-12-05 14:54:53','',89,'http://mapping-cotech.test.outlandish.com/89-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
