olor: #252525; font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Print finishing</b></span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #252525; font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Printing</b></span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #252525; font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Web design</b></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Chapel Street Studio','','publish','closed','closed','','chapel-street-studio','','','2017-01-25 21:27:35','2017-01-25 21:27:35','',0,'http://mapping-cotech.test.outlandish.com/?post_type=co_op&#038;p=132',0,'co_op','',0),
