	(297,1,'2016-12-12 16:24:15','2016-12-12 16:24:15','<h1 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>OUR MANIFESTO</b></h1>\\r\\n<h5 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The Cooperative Technologists believe that cooperatives serve their members most effectively, and strengthen the co-operative movement, by working together through local, national, regional and international structures.</h5>\\r\\n<h5 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">If you believe in the same things we do, you might want to consider joining the network!</h5>\\r\\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">1. We want to help improve the world</p>\\r\\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">2. We think all workers should be treated equally</p>\\r\\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">3. We want to create democracy, equality and diversity in the workplace</p>\\r\\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">4. We believe it is important to create positive social value</p>\\r\\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">5. We value the necessity of sharing skills, knowledge, services and more amongst each other</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h5 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">If you agree to all of the above, find out more about joining the network here.</h5>','Home Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','72-revision-v1','','','2016-12-12 16:24:15','2016-12-12 16:24:15','',72,'http://mapping-cotech.test.outlandish.com/72-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
