	(305,1,'2016-12-12 17:31:50','2016-12-12 17:31:50','If you would like to join the CoTech network then the first thing you mustdo is read our <a href=\"manifesto\">manifesto</a>!\\r\\n\\r\\nOther than that, below is a requirements checklist:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n 	<li>You must be a technical cooperative, or be practising cooperative principles with the idea of becoming a cooperative</li>\\r\\n 	<li>You must sign up to the values we present in ourmanifesto</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\nTo find out more about how you can join, just get in touch below.\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n\\r\\n&nbsp;','Join Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','246-revision-v1','','','2016-12-12 17:31:50','2016-12-12 17:31:50','',246,'http://mapping-cotech.test.outlandish.com/246-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(306,1,'2017-02-17 15:19:13','2017-02-17 15:19:13','We believe in a fairer world in which wealth and resources are distributed to the people who need them rather than those best able to take them.\n\nAs <a href=\"/about\">Co-operative Technologists</a> we aim to ensure that technology plays its part in creating a fairer world.\n\nOur individual worker co-operatives have shown that workers who collectively own their companies and control their destinies make better workplaces, better suppliers and better digital products.\n\nWe call upon tech workers who share our vision to <a href=\"/join\">join us</a>.\n\nWe call upon consumers of digital products - including trades unions, charities, governments and private companies - to reject the (false) assumption that only multinational conglomerates or private equity-funded startups can be great tech companies. Technology is the lifeblood of all our futures, not just a gravy train for the (fortunate) few.\n\nWe hereby give notice to technology companies that do not treat their employees fairly, do not give their workers control of their businesses and do not seek to create a fairer world that your days are numbered. We are more creative, more committed and more resilient. <a href=\"/join\">Join us</a>.','Manifesto','','inherit','closed','closed','','303-autosave-v1','','','2017-02-17 15:19:13','2017-02-17 15:19:13','',303,'http://mapping-cotech.test.outlandish.com/303-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
