	(320,1,'2016-12-12 18:01:12','2016-12-12 18:01:12','<p>We are the Cooperative Technologists (or CoTech for short); a group of tech coops who have formed together to make one large collection of cooperatives, inspired byPrinciple 6, <i>Cooperation amongst</i> cooperatives, taken from the seven Cooperative Principles.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>On 14th November 2016, we allmet in Sheffield, at the Workers Stately Home, Wortley Hall, some of us met for the very first time. We shared ideas, skills, needs and much, much more.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img src=\"https://wiki.coops.tech/w/images/a/ae/Pose.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"376\" />\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Now, ware attempting something that has neverbeen attempted before. A network that can grow together. A network that can share resources, skills, work and time. A networkpassionate about creating a work environment that is fair to all workers. A network that is motivated by a world keen to create justice, not profit.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Read our manifesto and if you would like to work with us, or join the network, you can get in touch here.</p>','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','248-revision-v1','','','2016-12-12 18:01:12','2016-12-12 18:01:12','',248,'http://mapping-cotech.test.outlandish.com/248-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
