	(347,1,'2016-12-16 16:52:59','2016-12-16 16:52:59','<p>The Cooperative Technologists believe that cooperatives serve their members most effectively, and strengthen the co-operative movement, by working together through local, national, regional and international structures.<p/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you believe in the same things we do, you might want to consider joining the network!</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>We want to help improve the world</li>\r\n	<li>We think all workers should be treated equally</li>\r\n	<li>We want to create democracy, equality and diversity in the workplace</li>\r\n	<li>We believe it is important to create positive social value</li>\r\n	<li>We value the necessity of sharing skills, knowledge, services and more amongst each other</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>If you agree to all of the above, find out more about joining the network <a href=\"join\">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p>If you would like to read more about us, please click <a href=\"about\">here</a>.</p>','Manifesto','','inherit','closed','closed','','303-revision-v1','','','2016-12-16 16:52:59','2016-12-16 16:52:59','',303,'https://dev.coops.tech/303-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(348,1,'2016-12-16 16:53:06','2016-12-16 16:53:06','<p>The Cooperative Technologists believe that cooperatives serve their members most effectively, and strengthen the co-operative movement, by working together through local, national, regional and international structures.<p/>\r\n\r\n<p>If you believe in the same things we do, you might want to consider joining the network!</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>We want to help improve the world</li>\r\n	<li>We think all workers should be treated equally</li>\r\n	<li>We want to create democracy, equality and diversity in the workplace</li>\r\n	<li>We believe it is important to create positive social value</li>\r\n	<li>We value the necessity of sharing skills, knowledge, services and more amongst each other</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>If you agree to all of the above, find out more about joining the network <a href=\"join\">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p>If you would like to read more about us, please click <a href=\"about\">here</a>.</p>','Manifesto','','inherit','closed','closed','','303-revision-v1','','','2016-12-16 16:53:06','2016-12-16 16:53:06','',303,'https://dev.coops.tech/303-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(349,1,'2016-12-16 16:54:01','2016-12-16 16:54:01','<p>If you would like to join the CoTech network then the first thing you mustdo is read our <a href=\"manifesto\">manifesto</a>!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Other than that, below is a requirements checklist:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You must be a technical cooperative, or be practising cooperative principles with the idea of becoming a cooperative</li>\r\n	<li>You must sign up to the values we present in ourmanifesto</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>To find out more about how you can join, just get in touch below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also read more about us <a href=\"about\">here</a>.','Join','','inherit','closed','closed','','246-revision-v1','','','2016-12-16 16:54:01','2016-12-16 16:54:01','',246,'https://dev.coops.tech/246-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(350,1,'2016-12-16 16:54:35','2016-12-16 16:54:35','<p>We are the Cooperative Technologists (or CoTech for short); a group of tech coops who have formed together to make one large collection of cooperatives, inspired byPrinciple 6, <i>Cooperation amongst</i> cooperatives, taken from the seven Cooperative Principles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On 14th November 2016, we allmet in Sheffield, at the Workers Stately Home, Wortley Hall, some of us met for the very first time. We shared ideas, skills, needs and much, much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://wiki.coops.tech/w/images/a/ae/Pose.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"376\" />\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, we are attempting something that has neverbeen attempted before:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A network that can grow together. A network that can share resources, skills, work and time. A networkpassionate about creating a work environment that is fair to all workers. A network that is motivated by a world keen to create justice, not profit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Read our <a href=\"manifesto\">manifesto</a>, and if you would like to work with us, or join the network, you can get in touch <a href=\"join\">here</a>.</p>','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','248-revision-v1','','','2016-12-16 16:54:35','2016-12-16 16:54:35','',248,'https://dev.coops.tech/248-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
