	(2149,30,'2017-05-26 14:37:27','2017-05-26 14:37:27','We are an immersive media workers\' co-operative specialising in virtual, augmented and mixed reality.\r\n\r\nOur projects range from art, through simulations and education to strictly practical applications.\r\n\r\nWe embody the world where only imagination is the limit. We never settle for the mediocre. We aim to stimulate empathy and demonstrate that what\'s equitable is not only ethically compelling, it is also more efficient.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to engaging in cutting-edge endeavours that build bridges across disciplines and environments in order to bring people together.\r\n\r\nLet\'s forge alliances for the future we want to live in.','Animorph','','inherit','closed','closed','','1972-revision-v1','','','2017-05-26 14:37:27','2017-05-26 14:37:27','',1972,'https://www.coops.tech/1972-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
